ZH: 这个记号是重要的线索。
EN: This mark is an important clue.

ZH: 我在地图上用红色记号标记了我们的目的地。
EN: I marked our destination on the map with a red mark.

ZH: 在这本书上，我用彩色记号做了笔记。
EN: In this book, I took notes with colored marks.

ZH: 他把字典里陌生单词用记号圈起来。
EN: He circled unfamiliar words in the dictionary with marks.

ZH: 那些小圆圈是老师在考试卷上的记号。
EN: Those small circles are the marks made by the teacher on the exam paper.

ZH: 请把重要的地方用记号标出来。
EN: Please mark the important places with marks.

ZH: 这个记号表明这件物品已经审查过了。
EN: This mark indicates that this item has been inspected.

ZH: 我找不到我在文件上做的记号了。
EN: I can't find the marks I made on the document.

ZH: 做记号是为了让事物更易于辨认。
EN: Making marks is to make things easier to identify.

ZH: 这个记号意味着搭乘巴士要付费。
EN: This mark means that bus rides require payment.

ZH: 老师在纸上用记号标明了错题。
EN: The teacher marked the wrong questions with marks on the paper.

ZH: 用记号把你想要记住的内容标出来。
EN: Mark the content you want to remember with marks.

ZH: 他沿路用记号做了标记，以便能够找到回家的路。
EN: He made marks along the way so he could find his way home.

ZH: 每个学生都有自己的记号来识别书包。
EN: Each student has their own mark to identify their backpack.

ZH: 这个记号代表了我们的团队。
EN: This mark represents our team.

ZH: 请在要修复的地方用记号标记。
EN: Please mark the places to be repaired with marks.

ZH: 在心情日记上，她用不同的记号表示不同的心情。
EN: She used different marks to represent different moods in her mood diary.

ZH: 我会在地图上用星星做记号，标记我们经过的有趣地点。
EN: I will mark interesting places we pass with stars on the map.

ZH: 这种记号是为了帮助读者更好地理解故事情节。
EN: This mark is meant to help readers better understand the story plot.

ZH: 这个记号可能是导演的暗示。
EN: This mark may be a hint from the director.
